o</td></tr><tr><td rowspan="1" colspan="1">1971</td><td rowspan="1" colspan="1">JC virus</td><td rowspan="1" colspan="1">polyoma</td></tr><tr><td rowspan="1" colspan="1">1971</td><td rowspan="1" colspan="1">Vaccinia virus</td><td rowspan="1" colspan="1">pox</td></tr><tr><td rowspan="1" colspan="1">1972</td><td rowspan="1" colspan="1">Bovine papular stomatitis virus</td><td rowspan="1" colspan="1">pox</td></tr><tr><td rowspan="1" colspan="1">1972</td><td rowspan="1" colspan="1">Mokola virus</td><td rowspan="1" colspan="1">rhabdo</td></tr><tr><td rowspan="1" colspan="1">1972</td><td rowspan="1" colspan="1">Monkeypox virus</td><td rowspan="1" colspan="1">pox</td></tr><tr><td rowspan="1" colspan="1">1972</td><td rowspan="1" colspan="1">Norwalk virus</td><td rowspan="1" colspan="1">calici</td></tr><tr><td rowspan="1" colspan="1">1972</td><td rowspan="1" colspan="1">Ross River virus</td><td rowspan="1" colspan="1">toga</td></tr><tr><td rowspan="1" colspan="1">1973</td><td rowspan="1" colspan="1">Bangui virus</td><td rowspan="1" colspan="1">bunya</td></tr><tr><td rowspan="1" colspan="1">1973</td><td rowspan="1" colspan="1">Dugbe virus</td><td rowspan="1" colspan="1">bunya</td></tr><tr><td rowspan="1" colspan="1">1973</td><td rowspan="1" colspan="1">Hepatitis A virus</td><td rowspan="1" colspan="1">picorna</td></tr><tr><td rowspan="1" colspan="1">1973</td><td rowspan="1" colspan="1">Kotonkan virus</td><td rowspan="1" colspan="1">rhabdo</td></tr><tr><td rowspan="1" colspan="1">1973</td><td rowspan="1" colspan="1">Rotavirus A</td><td rowspan="1" colspan="1">reo</td></tr><tr><td rowspan="1" colspan="1">1973</td><td rowspan="1" colspan="1">Tamdy virus</td><td rowspan="1" colspan="1">bunya</td></tr><tr><td rowspan="1" colspan="1">1974</td><td rowspan="1" colspan="1">Getah virus</td><td rowspan="1" colspan="1">toga</td></tr><tr><td rowspan="1" colspan="1">1975</td><td rowspan="1" colspan="1">B19 virus</td><td rowspan="1" colspan="1">parvo</td></tr><tr><td rowspan="1" colspan="1">